BIDDING - It does not really matter what you bid.  Just don&#39;t be stupid.<br />
<br />
THE FREE PEOPLE - There are a lot of mounts, because you never know who is going to play Dunland (I will spell that out for you - discard possesions).  Everyone needs to be mounted.  And for the most part get the Riders a Spear.  There is not Eomers spear because it isn&#39;t much better then a regular Spear.  Herugrum is there to add to Theodens vitality.  Eowyns Sword, because I have a few and I wanted to use one.  <br />
****Change Theoden to Son of Thengel****  My mistake.  Use SofT to liberate sites - thats what those pesky farmers are for.  Plus they can help you in a tight situation.  DON&#39;T forget that.<br />
Aside from that - the FREE PEOPLE ARE MADE TO RUN - NOT PLAY SILLY GAMES WITH MINIONS.  They are quick and strong - I side barred all other stategies at this time.<br />
<br />
MINIONS - Uruks are TRACKERS AND FOR THE MOST PART FIERCE.  That is why I have the conditions I do.  They are supposed to tick off the Opponent - prevent discarding Hobbits and stuff like that.  Put WEARY on the opponents BIG COMPANIONS.  DO NOT WASTE WEARY.  Then use the other conditions to discard the Opp&#39;s conditions and take control of sites.<br />
<br />
NOTE:  Everything in caps is important.  Don&#39;t just judge the deck by th cards.  <br />
